headline.main: TOP 25 REWIND: No. 5 Tar Heels Finish 2 Games Up in ACC
headline.print_headline: TOP 25 REWIND: No. 5 Tar Heels Finish 2 Games Up in ACC

lead_paragraph: North Carolina's win over rival Duke ended up putting the fifth-ranked Tar Heels two games better than anyone else in the rugged Atlantic Coast Conference. Coach Roy Williams is hoping that has his team prepared for what's to come.
